aboutEarrings.title: What's earrings?
aboutEarrings.body: An earring is a piece of jewelry attached to the ear via a piercing in the earlobe or another external part of the ear (except in the case of clip earrings, which clip onto the lobe).

aboutEarrings.title: Types of earring
aboutEarrings.body: 1) helix/cartilage 2) industrial 3) rook 4) daith 5) tragus 6) snug 7) conch 8) anti-tragus 9) lobe

aboutEarrings.title: What are earrings done from?
aboutEarrings.body: Earring components may be made of any number of materials, including metal, plastic, glass, precious stone, beads, wood, bone, and other materials.
